Type: Package
Package: MARCviz
Title: R Package for Meta-Analytic Rain Cloud (MARC) Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kaitlyn", "Fitzgerald", email = "kfitzgerald@apu.edu", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Avery", "Charles", email = "acharles20@apu.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("David", "Khella", email = "dkhella20@apu.edu", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Kaitlyn Fitzgerald <kfitzgerald@apu.edu>
Description: This package produces a Meta-Analytic Rain Cloud (MARC) Plot.
    The MARC plot displays the relative weight of each study while providing a summary effect on its own plane.
    This plot utilizes the y axis for weight and the x axis for standardized mean difference (SMD).
License: GPL (>= 3)
